description: This is skill allows an end user to get some basic facts about a game of corn hole. There is no special hardware required to use this skill.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask Pistol Pete to tell me a cornhole fact.
Alexa, ask Pistol Pete for a cornhole fact.
Alexa, ask Pistol Pete to give me a cornhole nugget.
name: Cornhole Nuggets
shortDescription: Ask Alexa for a Cornhole nugget/fact.
